# Your rule content

1.1 Directory Organization
app/: Contains Next.js App Router pages and layouts
Route-specific components should be in their respective route folders
API routes should be placed in app/api/
components/: UI components organized by purpose:
ui/: Basic UI components (buttons, inputs, etc.)
common/: Reusable components used across the application
layout/: Components defining structure and positioning
icons/: Icon components
auth/: Authentication-related components
lib/: Core functionality and utilities
agents/: Agent-related functionality
db/: Database connections and models
utils/: Utility functions
hooks/: Custom React hooks
tracing/: Tracing and monitoring logic
public/: Static assets
types/: TypeScript type definitions